      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently serviced for optimal variable valve timing. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to mitigate common fatigue. Riding on its original suspension geometry, the car provides the precise turn-in and feedback expected of the M-chassis. It is a well-maintained example that performs exactly as an M-car should, balancing high-RPM performance with a solid mechanical foundation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
