    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained, reliable SUV that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior is finished in a deep Midnight Blue that still holds a high-gloss shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and one small scuff on the rear bumper from city parking, the body is straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the cabin is appointed with slate gray leather upholstery that has been kept in excellent shape. The rear seats appear nearly new, while the driver\u2019s seat shows only light softening of the leather consistent with careful use. All interior electronics\u2014including the premium sound system, dual-zone climate control, and backup camera\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. I have kept a meticulous log of all oil changes and scheduled maintenance, including a recent brake pad replacement and a fresh set of all-season tires with plenty of tread remaining. This car has been smoke-free, pet-free, and garage-kept for the majority of its life. It delivers a quiet, comfortable ride and is ready for its next owner to drive it home with total confidence.",
